{"tid":2312092,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"金大仙區票后民主女神又黎搞分化","createTime":"2020-12-04T14:47:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-04T14:59:07.000Z","uid":129471,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"d6e7c9abb541fde38aaa49293b572a97f77904cf","tid":2312092,"uid":129471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:47:56.000Z","msg":"金大仙區龍蟠苑早兩日有班熱血街坊成功趕走左成20年歷史既建制法團: <br />\n<br />\n【龍蟠苑法團改選 現屆建制被踢走 街坊：好激動！】<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3683823425036584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fposts%2F3683823425036584&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=283a9b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/posts/3683823425036584</a><br />\n<br />\n龍蟠苑14街坊撼低現屆法團 居民激動嚎哭「終於等到呢一日」<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079207\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079207&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=f210e01f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1079207&h=ab94f546\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1079207</a><br />\n<br />\n班街坊等左依一日好耐，因為之前個法團真係出晒名衰格，所以今次對新既法團好有希望。<br />\n而果一區既票后民主女神譚香文就第一時間出post 抽水話恭喜佢地，希望同佢地合作咁話。<br />\n<br />\n早兩日其中一座有武肺確診case, 新果班委員即刻去果座到幫手同派物資。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lungpooninfo/posts/106921684602395\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flungpooninfo%2Fposts%2F106921684602395&d=y57o2ak4%2BKgx1hG4eir1w3r2%2BPVmRcyv9paqmPGdWjc%3D&h=1b68859a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lungpooninfo/posts/106921684602395</a><br />\n而第二日女神就出左封信俾新法團話要去果一座派&quot;高質&quot;口罩 : <br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/129016240_3526243307468579_6255884956865099541_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=ZslJaHHWkH0AX-nXlwa&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-1.fna&amp;oh=48b8751159313fdbb270a216c00d658d&amp;oe=5FF193D6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F129016240_3526243307468579_6255884956865099541_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DZslJaHHWkH0AX-nXlwa%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-1.fna%26oh%3D48b8751159313fdbb270a216c00d658d%26oe%3D5FF193D6&h=053dbdaf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/129846848_3526243410801902_5381484649619949390_o.jpg?_nc_cat=105&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=bhxRJgjlv80AX93INYx&amp;_nc_oc=AQnC9OJkz71zxT7KVMSxlwTky6mBBvTqY3jstITnFt3GUXTYxQZq4N2m0lpePZUVTQQ&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=dd0f8c4616170570aca08d44046ef216&amp;oe=5FEE4859\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F129846848_3526243410801902_5381484649619949390_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D105%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DbhxRJgjlv80AX93INYx%26_nc_oc%3DAQnC9OJkz71zxT7KVMSxlwTky6mBBvTqY3jstITnFt3GUXTYxQZq4N2m0lpePZUVTQQ%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Ddd0f8c4616170570aca08d44046ef216%26oe%3D5FEE4859&h=c690ddd1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n而法團回覆左就話唔好la，最主要原因法團剛接手幾日，未定到派野既規矩，就話如果有需要就叫居民去佢辦事署到拎，因為佢個辦事署係正屋苑商場入面，同埋大家居民都知新既法團如果俾得佢派就一定要俾埋其他人派，如果民建聯黎話派又無得say no? <br />\n<br />\n點知女神就即刻出post 玩分化人地龍蟠苑:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/m8LNTpy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fm8LNTpy.jpg&h=71f7d22c&s={SIZE}\" /> 頭先放工果陣仲要係地鐵站出口擺街站用大聲公係咁loop 唱鳩人地。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n龍街坊們想話聲佢聽佢有幾討厭係唔得，因為佢最出名係block 晒自己區o的選民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />. 星區既居民都唔明點解會有個咁既區議員........."},{"pid":"bd48e1108d6683c9025be8cc244d64488c419636","tid":2312092,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"成日講到佢有幾衰幾難合作 但佢有6千1票, 好似無人夠佢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9147ab5ae2596ead4998511bf1b53f8410a4c564","tid":2312092,"uid":132189,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd48e1108d6683c9025be8cc244d64488c419636","tid":2312092,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"成日講到佢有幾衰幾難合作 但佢有6千1票, 好似無人夠佢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:51:41.000Z","msg":"冇得揀先揀佢咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cc8e44a8112c3eb4545869c83ef7a316a6c9bbb","tid":2312092,"uid":370352,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"bd48e1108d6683c9025be8cc244d64488c419636","tid":2312092,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"成日講到佢有幾衰幾難合作 但佢有6千1票, 好似無人夠佢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:53:16.000Z","msg":"lesser evil <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ad0e3756b0c33c25d9d39937658ba27b7dca134","tid":2312092,"uid":62226,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:55:53.000Z","msg":"而家好憎啲區議員鳩派口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9543696c35cf7be05d31618cdb53ad8d6a2252a3","tid":2312092,"uid":129471,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd48e1108d6683c9025be8cc244d64488c419636","tid":2312092,"uid":192409,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-04T14:49:42.000Z","msg":"成日講到佢有幾衰幾難合作 但佢有6千1票, 好似無人夠佢多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"cit